text: Elaine H. Beech (born March 16, 1960) is an American politician. She was a member of the Alabama House of Representatives from the 65th District, serving since 2009. She is a member of the Democratic party. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:21st-century American politicians Category:Alabama Democrats Category:Living people Category:Members of the Alabama House of Representatives Category:People from Washington County, Alabama
